		<div id="comment_body_64429656">We don't really know! Maybe there are other life forms today that are the result of a previous merger. We just haven't identified them yet. Also this might have happened many times before, but their lineage didn't survive until today.</div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64429656">

</div>
